\dfrac13n(n-1)(n+1)
 P[M\leqslant k]=\frac{k}{n+1}\cdot\frac{k-1}{n}. 
 E[M]=\sum_{k=0}^{n}P[M\gt k]=n+1-\sum_{k=0}^{n}P[M\leqslant k]=n+1-\frac1{n(n+1)}\sum_{k=0}^{n}k(k-1). 
 E[M]=\frac23(n+2). 
